body: This branch supports utility code written in Cython with @cname() decorators.

commit.message: Support utility code written in Cython
Refactor the 'cython' cimport scope to use CythonUtilityCode
Make it possible to construct sub-magic-modules of cython
Test for problem with CythonUtilityCode overwriting __test__
Cython Utility Code cname extclass decorator + extmethod prototypes

title: Cython Utility Code
